data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 sides brick traditional ranch home nestled in the historic community of College Park. With a timeless appeal, this residence offers a perfect blend of classic architecture and modern conveniences.    As you enter, you are greeted by a formal living room and dining room, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or enjoying family dinners. The heart of the home lies in the large kitchen featuring an island, a generous sink, stainless steel appliances, and a delightful breakfast nook Co a culinary haven for any home chef.    The spacious family room is bathed in natural light, accentuating the warmth of the fireplace flanked by bookcases, providing a cozy spot to unwind and relax. Down the hall, discover a hall bath with double sinks and a walk-in tile shower, granting access to a large bedroom adorned with two closets.    The main level also hosts two additional bedrooms that share a Jack-and-Jill bathroom with a tub/shower combo, ensuring comfort and convenience for all residents. The thoughtful layout emphasizes both privacy and communal spaces, making it perfect for families and guests alike.    Venture downstairs to the finished terrace level, where practicality meets style. A large laundry room, a full guest bedroom, and a well-appointed bathroom with a shower await. The flexible space, ideal for an office or recreation room, adds versatility to the lower level.    The basement level boasts a three-car garage with expansive storage space, offering endless possibilities for a workshop or additional storage needs. The flat 0.67-acre homesite is adorned with established landscaping, creating a picturesque setting. The elongated driveway adds both convenience and curb appeal to this lovely property.    Conveniently located within walking distance from Barret Park, this home provides easy access to shopping, restaurants, and quick routes to the highway. Also located in the Woodward Academy School District! Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional residence in the heart of historical College Park Co where classic elegance meets modern comfort. Schedule your showing today!
